{"tid":2081883,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【天譴】長江流域暴雨釀洪災！半壁江山遭波及","createTime":"2020-06-27T14:41:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T15:32:07.000Z","uid":293677,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b67deb202a0d0bd5297194151f69f0fbc306bfd1","tid":2081883,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:41:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3210775\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3210775&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFugAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=67afd0b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3210775&h=93f86a30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3210775</a><br />\n<br />\n2020-06-27 20:38:16<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國西南部暴雨成災，近日雨水直灌長江流域，釀多地洪災，加上三峽大壩水位超出警戒線，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">長江上中下游約千座水庫急洩洪，不少地區被暴漲河水淹沒，其中，湖北宜昌災情頻傳，城區部份路段積水嚴重，交通要道堵塞。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n綜合中媒報導，根據中國應急管理部數據顯示，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">截至6月26日，全中國共有26個省（區、市）遭受洪災，受災人口1374萬人次，死亡失蹤81人，緊急轉移安置74.4萬人次，倒塌房屋1萬餘多間，直接經濟損失278億元（約新台幣1012億元）；中國目前已有15個省（區、市）84條河流發生超警戒水位以上洪水，其中，重慶市綦江區更出現近80年來最大洪災。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZkejTnV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZkejTnV.jpg&h=fc2593c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">唔好俾佢停</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee39d31da0f682964f63c9fcd5753bc804ea053","tid":2081883,"uid":35699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:41:59.000Z","msg":"唔信新唐人"},{"pid":"7078f9332fd3cb99d0951e4197c636ecff44d015","tid":2081883,"uid":212706,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:42:33.000Z","msg":"信政府，唔怕！"},{"pid":"8128a3cac9f0652e930228f6ec946d8caabb2d1c","tid":2081883,"uid":31542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:44:23.000Z","msg":"假新聞 無可能嘅事<br />\n天朝日日風和日麗"},{"pid":"f1890361a7fc6ca366adf4ced6c55f6a3fd79e12","tid":2081883,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:44:55.000Z","msg":"冇事既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b29f11af3efca74cd023c685ce7038527accde2c","tid":2081883,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8128a3cac9f0652e930228f6ec946d8caabb2d1c","tid":2081883,"uid":31542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:44:23.000Z","msg":"假新聞 無可能嘅事<br />\n天朝日日風和日麗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:45:15.000Z","msg":"香港就風和日麗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66f46a46bf594c7b1be35cd35097518eb9c44457","tid":2081883,"uid":58209,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:45:49.000Z","msg":"問我國家那像水災<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2e1d4c5f250428614b7da6201cac8cd9b09201","tid":2081883,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:45:52.000Z","msg":"扮咩，根本無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f988a159fd496c553bcac888842797ca72b61ea","tid":2081883,"uid":359300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:46:13.000Z","msg":"冇事嘅多難興邦吖嘛"},{"pid":"4b6c7dbf765a4c6a354149e011b838bbaf75ab0b","tid":2081883,"uid":25635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:48:58.000Z","msg":"今年赤字，唔知仲洗唔洗送錢上去振佢老母個joy <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228fed16f5230af16fd37af58ce51fb5e7bc6a34","tid":2081883,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T14:56:05.000Z","m